title: Sun Records: The 50th Anniversary Collection - 2002 2CD [flac]
description:
Sun Records: The 50th Anniversary Collection -2002 (2CD) [flac]

2002 was the 50th anniversary of the first Sun Records release, so they put out a great collection of 44 of their biggest hits. Elvis Presley, Carl Perkins, Jerry Lee Lewis, Roy Orbison, Johnny Cash and more of some of the best rock & roll and rockabilly players of the late 1950s and early 1960s.
